Subject: [PATCH] fix: add short URL /s/:hash route - fix 404 on Telegram short
 links

- Add src/app/s/[hash]/route.ts (REST API, no supabase-js dependency)
- Add src/app/api/s/[hash]/route.ts as backup route
- Update next.config.mjs image remotePatterns for coingecko
- Fix worker URLs from hashspring.com to www.hashspring.com

Root cause: short URL route files were created locally but never
committed to git, so Vercel deployment had no /s/ handler.

